formula: a(n) ~  n! * (-1)^(n+1) * c / (n^(3/2) * r^n), where r = 0.466059131659188864998662507... is the root of the equation log(1-r) + exp(-r) = 0, c = 0.543667388388591787444659334... = sqrt((1 - exp(-t))*(t + exp(t))/(2*Pi*t)), where t = 0.627470179597516584961148... is the root of the equation exp(t)*(1 + log(t)) = 1 . - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Feb 03 2015, updated Mar 22 2016
